---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
	title="Welcome to Cello"
	description="A transition page for visitors from GKC Consulting to Cello."
	bodyClass="welcome-page"
>
	<section class="page-hero">
		<div class="page-hero-inner narrow">
			<p class="eyebrow">Welcome</p>
			<h1>A stronger Cello for critical business systems.</h1>
			<p class="lead">
				GKC Consulting is becoming part of Cello. The capability, people and
				practical approach customers value are becoming part of Cello's broader
				service for enterprise networks and digital resilience.
			</p>
			<div class="actions">
				<a class="button dark" href="/">Go to Cello home</a>
				<a class="button dark" href="/contact">Talk to our team</a>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="section">
		<div class="split">
			<div class="copy">
				<p class="eyebrow">What changes</p>
				<h2>One Cello relationship, broader capability.</h2>
				<p>
					Cello remains focused on business-only networks and service excellence.
					This added capability strengthens how Cello can support visibility,
					security, automation and assurance around the systems clients rely on.
				</p>
			</div>
			<div class="copy">
				<p class="eyebrow">What stays steady</p>
				<h2>Continuity for customers and teams.</h2>
				<p>
					Existing conversations, specialist knowledge and delivery discipline
					continue with a clear path into Cello. The focus is calm, practical
					progress for complex environments.
				</p>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="cta">
		<div>
			<p class="eyebrow">Next step</p>
			<h2>Continue to Cello.</h2>
			<p>
				Explore business connectivity, service visibility and practical resilience
				support from the Cello team.
			</p>
		</div>
		<a class="button" href="/">Go to Cello home</a>
	</section>
</Layout>
